CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F466A1772655072
OL,3,CCouncil dismisses plans to build homes
OL,4,Cexclusively for Welsh speakers
OL,6,FThe proposal has gained support from
OL,7,Fsome residents in the area. Manon
OL,8,FWilliams, a resident of six years,
OL,9,Fbacked the idea, stating, "the Welsh
OL,10,Flanguage is already dying" and
OL,11,Fsuggested "it would be nice to house
OL,12,Fpeople that are willing (to learn) or
OL,13,FWelsh speakers already."
OL,15,FHowever, she also acknowledged the
OL,16,Fcomplexity of the issue, adding there
OL,17,Fis a "fine line" before such a move
OL,18,Fbecomes discriminatory.
OL,26,@tD@YpmtD@bpn
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G2/5
