FL,467,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F466A1772655072
OL,3,CCouncil dismisses plans to build homes
OL,4,Cexclusively for Welsh speakers
OL,6,FGareth Jones, who grew up in the
OL,7,Fvillage, also said the plan was "a
OL,8,Fgood idea" that demonstrates residents
OL,9,Fare "committed to the village." He
OL,10,Fadded, "We have to preserve the Welsh
OL,11,Flanguage, and first choice is Welsh
OL,12,F(speaking) people, in my opinion."
OL,14,FBut at a Planning Committee meeting on
OL,15,FMonday 2nd March, Gwynedd Council
OL,16,Fstated that planning policy in Wales
OL,17,Fmust not "introduce elements of
OL,18,Fdiscrimination based on their
OL,19,Flinguistic ability".
OL,26,@tD@ApmtD@Jpn
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G3/5
