PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F466A1772655072
OL,3,CCouncil dismisses plans to build homes
OL,4,Cexclusively for Welsh speakers
OL,6,FIn a statement they said policies and
OL,7,Fdecisions "should not seek to control
OL,8,Fhousing occupancy on linguistic
OL,9,Fgrounds. The use of a planning
OL,10,Fcondition to restrict occupancy of the
OL,11,Fhouses to Welsh speakers only would
OL,12,Ftherefore be unlawful."
OL,14,FDespite the rejection of the idea from
OL,15,FGwynedd Council, Deputy Welsh Language
OL,16,FCommissioner, Osian Llywelyn, said he
OL,17,Fis "eager" for more policies "that
OL,18,Fcontribute to strengthening these
OL,19,Fcommunities".
OL,26,@tD@WO]
