PN,46605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F466A1772655072
OL,3,CCouncil dismisses plans to build homes
OL,4,Cexclusively for Welsh speakers
OL,6,FHe said: "The sustainability of
OL,7,Fcommunities with a high density of
OL,8,FWelsh speakers is essential to the
OL,9,Ffuture of the language...
OL,11,F"It should also be noted that Gwynedd
OL,12,FCouncil already prioritises people
OL,13,Fwith a local connection, and the
OL,14,Fevidence suggests that this approach
OL,15,Fensures that a high percentage of
OL,16,Fthose who are allocated housing are
OL,17,FWelsh speakers."
OL,26,@yD@PO]
